snippet.title: Fall Up - Official Trailer | Game Devs of Color Expo 2024
snippet.description: Explore the vibrant world of Fall Up, and check out platforming gameplay in this trailer for the 2.5D puzzle-platformer game, coming to Steam in 2024. Take a leap into a lost world of mechanical wonders and embark on a hopping adventure with our adorable Labi! You need to traverse this cartoonish world with a variety of jumps and moves, meet squishy creatures and clumsy robots and reveal the secrets of this world.
